    "Aside from completely missing domains, we expected to find more publications on Linguistics, but we were only left with just one publication.",
    "We can see that a lot of domains still have a large room for exploration where ML processing of scanpaths might be a suitable solution.",
    "Multidisciplinary publications, i.e., publications categorized under more than one domain, could also be a promising research direction.",
    "The UpSet plot in Figure 4 shows that 52 publications out of 77 were categorized under just one domain.",
    "This can be further supported by the fact that most of the remaining 25 publications had an intersection with Information Technology due to focusing mainly on the technology rather than the task, which left even fewer pure multidisciplinary publications."
